sentence: what is the tallest mountain in the united states ?
sentence-with-vars: what is the tallest mountain in the united states ?
sql: select mountain.mountain_name from mountain where mountain.mountain_altitude = ( select max ( mountain.mountain_altitude ) from mountain ) ;
